Cell.Text: You're going to be my Shield-Sister?
[S] So I'm told. Try and keep up.
[S] So I'm told. Let's see if you impress.

Node.Caption: C01FollowMeTopic: You're going to be my Shield-Brother?

Cell.Text: Ysgramor was the hero who started the Companions. Wuuthrad was his weapon. | He came from the ancient homeland and killed all the elves. | But not all of them, because some of them are still here.
It was the blade hefted by Ysgramor when he returned to drive the elves out of the old Skyrim. | Without that axe, this whole land would be overrun still.

Wuuthrad is a relic of Ysgramor. Through that weapon, we trace our line straight to the first harbinger of makind in this land. | What fragments we have are displayed in honor, but we always seek more.
I watch you to make sure you are honorable. | If you are honorable and strong, then I can call you brother.
I watch you to make sure you are honorable. | If you are honorable and strong, then I can call you sister.
I would hope that's obvious. | Do well here, and you'll be a full member of the Companions. | Fail, and it won't matter anyway.

Node.Caption: C01ObserverTrialTopic: Why did Skjor call this my Trial?

Cell.Text: Bad people who don't like werewolves. | So they don't like us either.
A group of werewolf hunters who have gotten wise to our little secret. | They've made it their mission to hunt us down, but we are hunters ourselves.
Not everyone, but all the Circle are. It's a secret to everybody.
Not all of us, just the members of the Circle. We shouldn't be talking about this anyway.
A smart man came and told us about a blade piece. | Skjor thinks you should find it, and I'm supposed to watch you.

One of those icebrains who wanders the land getting people's hopes up. | From my view, I don't think we'll find anything here. | You'd better hope there's still a chance for you to prove yourself, though, or this Trial might last longer than you'd like.
I'm... I'm sorry you had to see that.
I hope I didn't scare you.
It's a blessing given to some of us. We can be like wild beasts. Fearsome.
Come on now, you're a sharp one. You must have heard of werewolves before. | It's a blessing given to the most honored of the Companions.
Oh, no. Only the Circle have the beastblood. Prove your honor to be a Companion. | "Eyes on the prey, not the horizon."
No, only members of the Circle get this blessing. Right now we're just seeing if you're worth keeping around.

Node.Caption: C01ObserverWhatNowBoss: You're going to make me a werewolf?

Cell.Text: I hope you've readied yourself.
[S] G|We should keep moving. Still the draugr to worry about.
[S] G|Now let's move. I think that was the last of the Silver Hand, but still plenty of draugr for the both of us.
[S] G|Don't delay, Shield-Brother.
[S] G|Don't delay, Shield-Sister.

Node.Caption: C01ObserverDismissalBranchTopic: I'll meet you at Dustman's Cairn.
